    <title>机器学习</title>
    <link href="/2022/04/01/pa/"/>
    <url>/2022/04/01/pa/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="ML"><a href="#ML" class="headerlink" title="ML"></a>ML</h1><h2 id="Pandas基础知识"><a href="#Pandas基础知识" class="headerlink" title="Pandas基础知识"></a>Pandas基础知识</h2><ol><li>将路径path中的文件读取到file: 将路径path中的文件读取到file: <code>file = pd.read_csv()</code></li><li>观察file文件中都有哪些列: <code>file.columns</code></li><li>舍弃空值数据: <code>file = file.dropna(axis=0)</code>  (记忆na:not available)</li><li>选择需要预测的列如Price：<code>y = file.Price</code></li><li>选择用来预测的列项：<br> <code>features = [&#39;Rooms&#39;, &#39;Bathroom&#39;, &#39;Landsize&#39;]</code><br> <code>X = file[features]</code></li><li>预览效果：<code>X.describe()</code> 或 <code>X.head()</code></li></ol><h1 id="scikit-learn库-sklearn"><a href="#scikit-learn库-sklearn" class="headerlink" title="scikit-learn库(sklearn)"></a>scikit-learn库(sklearn)</h1><h2 id="建模步骤："><a href="#建模步骤：" class="headerlink" title="建模步骤："></a>建模步骤：</h2><ol><li>Define: 定义数据类型，decision tree</li><li>Fit：调试模型，核心部分</li><li>Predict：预测结果</li><li>Evaluate：评估准确性</li></ol><h3 id="建模及输出Ex"><a href="#建模及输出Ex" class="headerlink" title="建模及输出Ex:"></a>建模及输出Ex:</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> sklearn.tree <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> DecisonTreeRegressor  <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># Define model. Specify a number for random_state to ensure same results each run  </span><br>model = DecisonTreeRegressor(random_state=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)  <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 调试模型  </span><br>model.fit(X,y)  <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 输出展示</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Making predictions for the following 5 houses:&quot;</span>)  <br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(X.head())  <br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;The predictions are&quot;</span>)  <br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(model.predict(X.head()))  <br>```    <br>最简单的评估算法：Mean Absolute Error(MAE), 即对预测值与实际值差值的绝对值求和取均值。  <br>简单的例子：  <br>``` python  <br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> sklearn.metrics   <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> mean_absolute_error  <br>predicted_home_prices = model.predict(X)  <br>mean_absolute_error(y, predicted_home_prices)  <br>```  <br>但是这其中存在一个很大的问题：应当在模型建立时排除掉一些数据，而在检测时用这些并未参与建模过程的新数据去检测。  <br>解决方法：利用sklearn中的train_test_split函数将数据分为两块。<br>Code：<br>  ```python   <br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> sklearn.model_selection <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> train_test_split  <br><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">#将数据分为训练数据和验证数据，分别用于建模和目标，为random_state赋值以保证每次运行得到相同的两组数据。  </span><br>  train_X,val_X, train_y, val_y = train_test_split(X, y, random_state=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>)   <br>  <span class="hljs-comment">#定义模型  </span><br>  model = DecisonTreeRegressor()  <br>  <span class="hljs-comment">#调试模型  </span><br>  model.fit(train_X, train_y)   <br>  <span class="hljs-comment">#输出预测值  </span><br>  val_predictions = model.predict(val_X)  <br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(mean_absolute_error(val_y, val_predictions))<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="一个新的模型：random-forests"><a href="#一个新的模型：random-forests" class="headerlink" title="一个新的模型：random forests"></a>一个新的模型：random forests</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> sklearn.ensemble <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> RandomForestRegressor  <br>```  <br><span class="hljs-comment">## 完整程序：  </span><br>```python  <br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> pandas <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> pd  <br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> sklearn.tree <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> DecisonTreeRegressor  <br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> sklearn.ensemble <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> RandomForestRegressor  <br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> sklearn.model_selection <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> train_test_split  <br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> sklearn.metrics <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> mean_absolute_error  <br><br>iowa_file_path = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;../input/train.csv&#x27;</span>  <br>home_data = pd.read_csv(iowa_file_path)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># creat features and target</span><br>y = home_data.SalePrice  <br>features = [<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;LotArea&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;YearBuilt&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;1stF1rSF&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;2ndF1rSF&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Fullbath&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;BedroomAbvGr&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;TotRmsAbvGrd&#x27;</span>]  <br>train_X, val_X, train_y, val_y = train_test_split(X,y,random_state=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)  <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># Specify Model and Fit it  </span><br>iowa_model = DecisonTreeRegressor(random_state=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)  <br>iowa_model.fit(train_X,train_y)  <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># Predict and Evaluate  </span><br>val_predictions = iowa_model.predict(val_X)  <br>val_mae = mean_absolute_error(val_predictions, val_y)  <br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Validation MAE when not specifying max_leaf_nodes: &#123;:,.0f&#125;&quot;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(val_mae))  <br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># function to find the max_leaf_nodes    </span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">get_mae</span>(<span class="hljs-params">max_leaf_nodes, train_X, val_X, train_y, val_y</span>):<br>  model = DecisonTreeRegressor(max_leaf_nodes=max_leaf_nodes, random_state=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)  <br>  model.fit(train_X, train_y)  <br>  val_predictions = model.predict(val_X)  <br>  mae = mean_absolute_error(val_predictions, val_y)  <br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>(mae)  <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># The best tree size</span><br>candidate_max_leaf_nodes = [<span class="hljs-number">5</span>,<span class="hljs-number">25</span>,<span class="hljs-number">50</span>,<span class="hljs-number">100</span>,<span class="hljs-number">250</span>,<span class="hljs-number">500</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1000</span>]  <br>scores = &#123;leaf_size: get_mae(leaf_size, train_X, val_X, train_y, val_y) <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> leaf_size <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> candidate_max_leaf_nodes&#125;  <br>best_tree_size = <span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(socres, key = scores.get)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># Using best value for max_leaf_nodes</span><br>best_iowa_model = DecisonTreeRegressor(max_leaf_nodes=best_tree_size, random_state=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)  <br>best_val_predictionsiowa_model.fit(train_X, train_y)  <br>best_val_predictions = best_iowa_model.predict(val_X)  <br>best_val_mae = mean_absolute_error(best_val_predictions, val_y)  <br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Validation MAE for best value of max_leaf_nodes: &#123;:,.0f&#125;&quot;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">float</span>(best_val_mae))  <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># Random Foreset Model  </span><br>rf_model = RandomForestRegressor(random_state=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)  <br>rf_model.fit(train_X, train_y)  <br>rf_val_predictions = rf_model.predict(val_X)  <br>rf_val_mae = mean_absolute_error(rf_val_predictions, val_y)  <br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Validation MAE for Random Foreset Model: &#123;:,.0f&#125;&quot;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(rf_val_mae))<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 基于全部数据建立一个新模型并将预测结果输出至Output.to_csv</span><br>rf_model_on_full_data = RandomForestRegressor(random_state=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)  <br>rf_model_on_full_data.fit(X, y)  <br>test_data_path = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;../input/test.csv&#x27;</span>  <br>test_data = pd.read_csv(test_data_path)  <br>test_X = test_data[features]<br>test_preds = rf_model_on_full_data.predict(test_X)  <br>output = pd.DataFrame(&#123;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Id&#x27;</span>: test_data.Id, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;SalePrice&#x27;</span>: test_preds&#125;)  <br>output.to_csv(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Output.csv&#x27;</span>, index=<span class="hljs-literal">False</span>)  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
